                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 85vb l.1: Ownership note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"> Fol. 85vb: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘቄስ፡ ተስፋ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ሣምራ፡ ዘሰረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡ ውጉዝ፡ ይኩን።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 85vb: This book is of priest Täsfa Śəllase (of) Śamra. The one who stole it or the one who scratched (what is written in it), shall be excommunicated. </q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"> Fol. 93rb l.7: ˀAsmat-prayer.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 93rb l.7: በስመ፡ አብ፡ በል፡ ከል፡ ተከልከል ፯ጊዜ፡ ሔጄርጄ፡ ፯ጊዜ፡ ጉሐጄን፡ ወጉበርጄን፯ጊዜ፡…</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"> </q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title of Text I is crudely written on the front leather cover with yellow paint.&#xD;
- Titles of the works (fols. 8r መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡ Mälkǝʾa Maryam, fol. 9r (መልክአ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ Mälkǝʾa ʾIyäsus) are crudely written in blue pen in the upper margins.&#xD;
- Short ownership note (ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘማይ፡ አንበሳ፡) is crudely written in a recent hand, below Additio 1: fol. 85vb.&#xD;
- Note, correction (?) written in the upper margin of fol. 90vb.&#xD;
- Several corrections written interlineally: e.g., fols. 6ra, 32vb, 60rb, 67rb, 90vb, 91ra. &#xD;
- Writing excercise: fols. 1r, 7v, 8r, 25r, 93v.&#xD;
- Pen trials: fols. 48r, 48v, 50r, 50v, 51v, 55r, 61v, 93v.</item>
